{"word":"G4437 - πυκνός - pyknós - pook-nos' - Often","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυκνός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pyknós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pook-nos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Often</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அநேகந்தரம், அடிக்கடி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"often more frequently, the more often"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G4635 - σκηνοποιός - skēnopoiós - skay-nop-oy-os'/4635\">G4635</a>; <i>clasped</i> (<i>thick</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>frequent</i>; neuter plural (as adverb) <i>frequently:</i> - often (-er).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}